reviewText: Greatest season ever! Greatest summer ever! Greatest baseball video wish they had this on their mets history dvd box set but yea yea we know the music copyrights crap wouldn't include it! So we the hardcore fans suffer for it! Goes to show you ...
I wish that 1986 mets a year to remember have dvd than vhs, also closed captioned for deaf

Hell, I hate the Mets....actually I can't stand them.  But, this is the greatest baseball season video ever, leading up to the world series.  The production of this video is uncomparable.  It changed my life, and will definitley change yours.

WILD BOYS, WILD BOYS!!!
